---
title: Garlic and Herb-Dressed Striploin Steak  with Heirloom Tomato Salad
description: A herbaceous heirloom tomato and pear salad with chives, lemon zest and goat cheese will dance on your tongue, while tender and luxurious sirloin steaks melts in your mouth. This premium weeknight meal is one for the 'gram!

